asset_contract.name: Sticky DAO
asset_contract.description:
DO NOT BUY ABOVE .089 ETH. New Sticky can be minted through the contract for 0.089 ETH. Become one of potentially 8,888 Sticky on the Ethereum blockchain. No utility, no promises, just vibes. 

**Sticky** is a gaming focused community of collectors here to **Stick Around™** in the metaverse. Sticky pfps allow you to access a token gated Discord channel in the **The Web3 Game** community. 

Owning one or more Sticky NFTs grants access to exclusive perks. This could be early access to web3 games in early/beta/alpha development stage. Whitelist raffle opportunities (free and paid mints) for in-game NFT collectibles from games launched around the globe. And possibly more in the future ahead.

The Web3 Game is your source for gaming news with blockchain elements. We cover crypto games and blockchain games with GameFi, DAO, crypto, and NFT integrations in various forms. While we do cover play to earn (P2E) content too, we focus less on the investment and speculation side.

asset_contract.name: No Strings Attached
asset_contract.description:
"No Strings Attached" is a groundbreaking digital art collection by Mac. Each piece is crafted using AI and is inspired by the principles of string theory.

The collection masterfully blends the rough, uneven landscapes found across our planet with elements that suggest fluidity and motion.

Central to these works are visual representations of energy strings, illustrating the oscillating frequencies that intertwine to construct the physical reality we experience.
